org.schema.game.mod.listeners

Interface ModListener

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BlockInitializationListener, NetworkInitializationListener, PlayerStateListener, SegmentControllerListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Mod

    public interface ModListener
    The superinterface for all listeners in the modding API. Every listener of the modding API will have to extend from or implement this interface.
